Turkish unit of  Ford Motor Co. (F)  in partnership with  Koc Holding
AS (KCHOL) , plans to pay an interim dividend of 217.2 million liras
($117 million), or 0.619 lira gross per share, on Oct. 27.  Ford Otosan will hold an extraordinary shareholdersâ€™
meeting on Oct. 25 for the approval of the dividend plan, it
said in a statement to the Istanbul Stock Exchange after the
